headline: The Home Depot and Google Cloud Launch Agentic AI Tools to Help Customers and Associates Bring Projects from 'How-to' to 'Done'
summary: Today at NRF 2026, The Home Depot and Google Cloud announced an expansion of their strategic partnership, further advancing the interconnected retail experience with new agentic AI tools that provide real-time, expert assistance to homeowners and professional customers (pros) like contractors, renovators and remodelers.

headline: 5 Considerations In The Upcoming CPI Report
summary: Stock indices rallied despite limited CPI data last month; since then, small-caps and Dow are outperforming tech into early 2026.
